cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.EC, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with pricing mechanisms in matching markets, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT). It also involves algorithms for optimization (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the form of the ascending price auction. The concept of revenue maximization is related to computational economics (cs.EC) and the use of approximation algorithms falls under machine learning (cs.LG).
